front.title: •Compact Firepower
front.gametext: If your warrior just fired a DH-17 blaster or scout blaster during a battle, draw destiny: (0) no effect, (1-3) target may not use weapons this turn, (4+) target is power and forfeit = 0 this battle.
front.lore: The small blasters used by biker scouts can be fired when piloting a vehicle at high speed.
